# Quality Workflow

- Always run `uv run poe check` after making any change and fix all errors before proceeding.
- Never commit or push — the user handles all git operations explicitly.
- Add new dependencies with `uv add <package>` (updates both `pyproject.toml` and `uv.lock`).
- Ruff is configured with line-length 100, target Python 3.10, and extends to notebooks.
- `gitleaks` pre-commit hook blocks commits containing secrets — never hardcode credentials.
